Package: PAGe
Type: Package
Title: Seasonal Flu Curve Alignment and Forecasting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Lennon", "Li", email = "lennon.li@oahpp.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("ChatGPT", "CoAuthor", role = "aut"))
Description: Align partially observed seasonal positivity curves to a learned reference
  shape via profile likelihood (shift tau and optional dilation delta), then forecast
  the remainder of the season with sensible prediction intervals and peak timing.
